svg.title: {\displaystyle {\begin{aligned}V({\text{take only B}})&=P({\text{1M in box B}}|{\text{take only B}})\times \$1,000,000+P({\text{nothing in box B}}|{\text{take only B}})\times \$0\\&=0.99\times \$1,000,000+0.01\times \$0=\$990,000\\V({\text{take both boxes}})&=P({\text{1M in box B}}|{\text{take both boxes}})\times \$1,001,000+P({\text{nothing in box B}}|{\text{take both boxes}})\times \$1,000\\&=0.01\times \$1,001,000+0.99\times \$1,000=\$11,000\end{aligned}}}
